Elasticity decomposition at the US point (tau=0.35):
  Intensive Frisch eps^int = alpha/(alpha+(1-tau)) = 1.32/1.97 = 0.670
  (this is the model-implied individual intensive Frisch at US)
  CGM 2011 consensus: ~0.30 -- the model's individual intensive elasticity is HIGHER
  than the CGM consensus; the model can match aggregate Frisch only because
  P also moves with tau, contributing an extensive component to the aggregate response.
